{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, we can test the teacher's understanding separately to distinguish between the teacher's own understanding and their ability to transfer that understanding to the student.",
    "We then suggest the reformulated test for scientific understanding transfer:",
    "The student takes an initial test, interacts with the teacher, and then takes a second test.",
    "While the second test should cover the same material or aspects, it should contain different questions to ensure the validity of the test.",
    "The extent to which the student's score increases on the second test is an indication of the teacher's ability to effectively phenomenon P to the student."
  ]
}